data.description: Enjoy total comfort and convenience within this delightful 4-bedroom, 4-bathroom Duluth home.  Located near historic downtown Duluth... Beautifully & thoughtfully renovated contemporary home. Its inviting living spaces, modern kitchen with a boat sink, and enclosed backyard create an ideal environment for everyday life and hosting guests. Featuring 2 fully functional kitchens, 2 fireplaces for warming up on cold nights and a 2-tiered deck made from Trex wood and fully fenced in backyard.  Let's not forget the In-law or rental suite.    Upgrade highlights: Newly renovated kitchen, premium flooring on top and bottom levels, NEW front & back custom decks (w/ underneath storage), newer roof (2023) newer siding (2023),  newer gutters (2023) newer HVAC systems (2021), newer water heater (2022).  Other upgrades completed within the last 4 years.  Huge garage... plenty of room for 2 cars, a workshop/ cave, plus more storage. This home will "WOW" you. It is a "must-see" to experience how "perfectly move-in ready" the home is. The property has been meticulously maintained & well cared for.  This home offers effortless access to entertainment, dining, and cultural attractions and an added bonus of no HOA.
